Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,REICHWEIN PSYCHIATRIC CENTER\N(MUNICH)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-You haven't had any alcohol since then?\N-I haven't even had a sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.51,0:00:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't drink alcohol,\Nyou're a man that can start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can drink alcohol,\Nwhat with me meeting you once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be struck by lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I provide respectable counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't even have time for drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first big job\Nsince becoming a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A big job?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what do you think of this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Using your physiognomy skills,\NDr. Reichwein,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of man is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Physiognomy, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard, are you mistaking me\Nfor some kind of fortune-teller?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're a sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They say you can see personalities\Nwith just one look at their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.52,0:01:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the result of\Nmeeting clients over many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then use the result of those meetings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to see if this man is a swindler.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A swindler?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the face of a swindler.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he tried,\Nhe'd be found out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about\Nthe possibility of suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.55,0:01:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide is very unlikely\Nwith a face like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,With how certain you sound,\Nyour physiognomy is strangely convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the result of my meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why are you asking about this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans Georg Schuwald…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know this name, right, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the rich one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the Vampire of Bavaria, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My client is that extremely rich man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He says that the man\Nin this photo, Edmund Fahren,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is his own son, of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See, he was found out right away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Schuwald completely believed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He deceived him quite skillfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through a lot to ascertain this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,However, one mystery still remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he know about the existence\Nand background of Schuwald's son
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to convince Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask the man himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, this man\Nhas already committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal, Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we old friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let me see\NEdmund Fahren's suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The handwriting analysis is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It is beyond a doubt\Nthat he wrote it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no reason to show\Nan outsider like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl Neuman and Lotte Frank\Ndiscovered the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They know Fahren\Nfrom his part-time job, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as always?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, even several more of me\Nwouldn't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After taking over for you,\NI've barely rested at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Blockhead Martin's finally a bigwig now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-I won't let you call me that anymore.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're no longer boss and subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Martin…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you don't know how much trouble\Nwe went through back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that time, we were so close\Nto catching that serial killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but you were drunk and shot him to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We went through so much\Ncleaning up that mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the time\Nto deal with a simple suicide case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to visit the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You preserved it properly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really, since it's not a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already given the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably moving out\Nthe deceased's belongings today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When did Blockhead Martin\Nbecome so efficient?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I got here in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But the movers are coming soon\Nto remove everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it'll only be two or three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is the pipe\Nhe hung the rope on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He wrote his last words on this desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the thesis he was writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Birth of Tragedy. Process and Reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Psychology of Ideologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. This bookcase is\Nwhat a philosophy student would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This section must be\Nreference materials for his thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this The Gallic Wars?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this one unrelated book here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Spanish? No, Latin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This book is clean,\Nexcept for this one underlined part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Room 204… Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bring more cardboard boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:06:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start by\Npacking the books into boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do with this desk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-That goes over here.\N-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask a bit about\Nthe room next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've shared everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not with the police.\NI'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever you are, you're bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My report is due tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but I haven't been able to concentrate\Nat all with the commotion next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then I'll just ask one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Were these two\Nclose with Fahren next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen them\Nin this boarding house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy next door\Ndidn't seem to have many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're done now, right?\N-Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you translate this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The underlined part.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fail my class,\Nyou better take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can no longer…"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"…deceive others."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't I done enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can no longer deceive others."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard this somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like this spot too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're Johan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see the scenery\Nmuch better from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, this is kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get down from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to get down! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At this hour, people start turning on\Ntheir lights at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Families are returning home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of dinner\Ncomes from out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always longed for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Longed for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, ever since I was a kid,\NI didn't have that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of family did you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that was insensitive of me to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was taken in\Nby foster parents when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, can I hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This was so trivial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can no longer deceive others."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was written in Fahren's suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was no suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All he did was translate this one line\Nin the book and write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my upbringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It got a bit depressing though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like\NI can talk to you about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the incredibly rich father\Nyou mentioned in your story just now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Schuwald, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crying
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been taking care of Schuwald,\Nand he's really worrying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't been eating properly\Nsince Fahren's suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, that guy will die next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl, how about telling him\Nthat you're his real son?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wanted to see\Nwhat kind of person he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell him the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll probably think\NI'm just a man who is after his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of person Schuwald is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all money to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't understand my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your real father is suffering\Nin the depths of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I have a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can no longer deceive others."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The words Fahren left\Nwere no suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He had simply translated
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the part underlined in The Gallic Wars,\Na book in his room written in Latin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems this wasn't a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just my intuition\Nfrom my many years in the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Mr. Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that's enough now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If his death wasn't a suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,your life may be in danger as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He was my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I report this last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His birthplace and upbringing\Nhave no connection to you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an imposter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that Fahren was a good guy\Nand not the type to swindle others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But he actually tried to trick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The master is feeling tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take your leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to end the investigation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not because this is\Nmy first big payment since I changed jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of great malice\Nhiding in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In life…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In life, there are some things\Nwith which you never get a second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This investigation isn't over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Convention on the Rights of the Child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You could call it\Na shared international pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect the rights\Nof vulnerable children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the topic\NI'm working with right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I volunteer to take care\Nof children from orphanages
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because I enjoy it,\Nrather than for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let us hear about\Nwhat you were saying before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Schuwald went bankrupt\Nthree times in the past and…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He went missing temporarily\Neach of those three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he appeared once more,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd be ferociously plotting his comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was reading books\Nfor my part-time job every Friday,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,he told me about this once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did he tell you where he'd disappear to?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So we just need to take him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a place\Nthat revitalizes them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like how you gaze upon\Nthe houses from the university rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuntz, it seems\Nthe sink drain is clogged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that sink over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, where's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you planning to do\Nto the master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The master has a visual impairment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're abducting him! Criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, the plan was a total success.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you planning to take me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're not Margot Langer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just want\Ninformation on the dead Fahren.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He showed up here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one is Fahren?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Which"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Two parties came to me\Nclaiming to be Schuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the blond one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the one with the black hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Black hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The one with the black hair\Ncame with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he brought\Na girl with him to a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A black-haired boy with a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that they were these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This young man
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,said that he is Schuwald's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you bring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The woods in Obernburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see the pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the fall leaves in the woods\Nlook beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, very.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And the wren?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear the chirps of the wren.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an industrial district now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen very closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Their chirps are so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many apples\Non the ground near the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What beautiful scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if the setting sun\Nhas made the fall leaves start burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's reflecting on the quiet surface\Nof the water, as if it were a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:21:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe such a view exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what did you say just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You said two parties appeared here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The black-haired youth\Nbrought a girl with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Fahren come alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the blond boy came with someone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fahren boy you mentioned\Ncouldn't speak properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The young man who called himself\Nhis friend gave me specifics.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to choose…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've believed him if he said\Nhe was Schuwald's son instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:06.39,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,400)\pos(360,340)}The Secret Woods
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:53.47,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(360,340)}Proof
